The evidence with the title 'Connecticut - Wikipedia ' says Connecticut is the southernmost state in the New England region of the United States . As of the 2010 Census, it has the highest per-capita income, Human Development Index ( 0.962 ) , and median household income in the UnitedStates.It is bordered by Rhode Island to the east , Massachusetts to the north, New  ... . Connecticut is slightly larger than the country of Montenegro . 
